  "title": "Junior Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>We’re an <strong>international outsourced sales and marketing company</strong>, working with brands across multiple industries to drive growth through high-impact, people-focused campaigns.</p><p>Not sure what’s next after graduating or ORD? Maybe you’re looking for something hands-on, fun, and full of growth. If that sounds like you — keep reading.<br />No experience needed. Just bring the enthusiasm.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Get to Do:</strong><br />🎡 Be part of exciting events and roadshows<br />🗣 Engage with people daily and sharpen your communication skills<br />💼 Learn valuable skills in a supportive, energetic team<br />🌍 Represent global brands and create lasting impressions</p><p><strong>What You’ll Get in Return:</strong><br />💰 Weekly payouts with unlimited commission<br />🎁 Performance-based incentives<br />📚 Hands-on training and skill-building workshops<br />🚀 Clear leadership pathways for career growth<br />✈️ Travel opportunities to broaden your exposure</p><p>Bring the energy — we’ll handle the training.<br />If you’re ready to start a fresh chapter, reach out and apply. There’s nothing to lose.</p>",
